{"title":"按钮","meta":{"title":"按钮","pubdate":"2012-12-12","filepath":"content/button.md","filename":"button","directory":"","id":"-button"},"body":"\n可直接拷贝代码使用\n\n<link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"screen\" href=\"dist/styles/main.css\">\n\n\n## 默认按钮\n\n````html\n<a class=\"pure-button\" href=\"#\">默认按钮</a>\n<button class=\"pure-button\">默认按钮</button>\n````\n\n## 已禁用按钮\n\n````html\n<a class=\"pure-button pure-button-disabled\" href=\"#\">不能点</a>\n<button class=\"pure-button pure-button-disabled\">不能点</button>\n````\n\n\n## 激活状态\n\n````html\n<a class=\"pure-button pure-button-active\" href=\"#\">激活状态</a>\n<button class=\"pure-button pure-button-active\">激活状态</button>\n````\n\n\n## 主要按钮\n\n````html\n<a class=\"pure-button pure-button-primary\" href=\"#\">主要按钮</a>\n<button class=\"pure-button pure-button-primary\">主要按钮</button>\n````\n\n\n## 自定义按钮\n\n````html\n<div>\n    <style scoped>\n\n        .button-success,\n        .button-error,\n        .button-warning,\n        .button-secondary {\n            color: white;\n            text-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .button-success:hover,\n        .button-error:hover,\n        .button-warning:hover,\n        .button-secondary:hover {\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .button-success {\n            background: rgb(28, 184, 65); /* this is a green */\n        }\n\n        .button-error {\n            background: rgb(202, 60, 60); /* this is a maroon */\n        }\n\n        .button-warning {\n            background: rgb(223, 117, 20); /* this is an orange */\n        }\n\n        .button-secondary {\n            background: rgb(66, 184, 221); /* this is a light blue */\n        }\n\n    </style>\n\n    <button class=\"button-success pure-button\">成功按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-error pure-button\">错误按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-warning pure-button\">警告按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-secondary pure-button\">次要按钮</button>\n</div>\n````\n\n## 不同尺寸\n\n````html\n<div>\n    <style scoped>\n\n        .button-xsmall {\n            font-size: 70%;\n        }\n\n        .button-small {\n            font-size: 85%;\n        }\n\n        .button-large {\n            font-size: 110%;\n        }\n\n        .button-xlarge {\n            font-size: 125%;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n\n    <button class=\"button-xsmall pure-button\">超小按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-small pure-button\">小按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"pure-button\">普通按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-large pure-button\">大按钮</button>\n    <button class=\"button-xlarge pure-button\">超大按钮</button>\n</div>\n````\n\n<script src=\"dist/scripts/jquery.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"dist/scripts/main.js\"></script>","abspath":"/Users/amoslee/Documents/nico/content/button.md","filepath":"content/button.md","filename":"button","directory":"","id":"-button","tags":[],"pubdate":"2012-12-12T00:00:00.000Z","status":"public","mtime":"2015-09-20T17:41:27.000Z","html":"<p>可直接拷贝代码使用</p>\n<link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"screen\" href=\"dist/styles/main.css\">\n\n\n<h2 id=\"默认按钮\">默认按钮</h2><div class=\"nico-insert-code\"><a class=\"pure-button\" href=\"#\">默认按钮</a>\n<button class=\"pure-button\">默认按钮</button></div><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"title\">a</span> <span class=\"attribute\">class</span>=<span class=\"value\">\"pure-button\"</span> <span class=\"attribute\">href</span>=<span class=\"value\">\"#\"</span>&gt;</span>默认按钮<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"title\">a</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"title\">button</span> <span class=\"attribute\">class</span>=<span class=\"value\">\"pure-button\"</span>&gt;</span>默认按钮<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"title\">button</span>&gt;</span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"已禁用按钮\">已禁用按钮</h2><div class=\"nico-insert-code\"><a class=\"pure-button pure-button-disabled\" href=\"#\">不能点</a>\n<button class=\"